        "subject": "LU-8336 osd-ldiskfs: add sanity check for ldiskfs journal size",
        "message": "LU-8336 osd-ldiskfs: add sanity check for ldiskfs journal size\n\nLustre need some metadata updates for a single transaction,\nwhich might declare more than 512 blocks credits, this need\nat least we have more than 4096 blocks journal size for RHEL7\n\nThis patch try to at least for 8192 blocks requirements for\njournal size.\n\nRHEL6 don't have problems because it limit max credits as 1/4\nof journal size, but RHEL7 codes limit it as 1/8 of journal size.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Shilong <wshilong@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I66b329054e793ccc0e5ff4d1af88ea8ef7baabf6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
